extends base.pug

block content
  .home
    .dark-bg
      .container
        .columns
          .column.is-8.is-offset-2
            .pitch.has-text-centered I'm a freelance web developer based in Boulder, Colorado. I design and build rich, responsive web applications and interactive user interfaces. I love working with teams full of curious, driven, and collaborative people. If you're looking to build something from scratch or you need support building out an existing system, let's talk.

    .container.has-text-centered
      .columns
        .column
          h3.title.is-2.has-text-centered(style="margin-top: 1em") Recent projects

      .columns.is-multiline
        .column.is-6
          .project
            div(style="border: 1px solid #ccc; height: 420px; overflow: hidden")
              img(src="/images/bob-ross-explorer.png")
            h4.title.is-4
              a(
                href="http://bob-ross-explorer.s3-website.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/#/"
                title="OneMove") The Bob Ross Explorer
            div.title.is-5 Vue.js + FiveThirtyEight data
        .column.is-6
          .project
            div(style="border: 1px solid #ccc; height: 420px; overflow: hidden")
              img(src="/images/terraform.png")
            h4.title.is-4
              a(
                href="https://medium.com/@adamdgibbons/amazon-virtual-private-clouds-with-terraform-an-introduction-tutorial-part-1-d369b6574835"
                title="OneMove") Amazon Virtual Private Clouds with Terraform:
                br
                | An Introduction &amp; Tutorial
            div.title.is-5 Medium article + Github demo repository

      h3.title.is-2.has-text-centered(style="margin-top: 1em") Past work

      .columns.is-multiline
        .column.is-4
          .project
            .logo
              img(src="/images/work/onemove/onemove-logo.png")
            h4.title.is-4
              a(
                href="/work/onemove"
                title="OneMove") OneMove
            div.title.is-5 Angular + Node + PostgreSQL
        .column.is-4
          .project
            .logo
              img(src="/images/work/moveline/moveline-logo.png")
            h4.title.is-4
              a(
                href="/work/moveline"
                title="Moveline") Moveline
            div.title.is-5 Angular + Node + MongoDB
        .column.is-4
          .project
            .logo
              img(src="/images/work/ics/ics-logo.png")
            h4.title.is-4
              a(
                href="/work/ics"
                title="ICS npm package") ICS
            div.title.is-5 NPM package
